{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":546,"text":"I was in New York during Hurricane Sandy,"},{"time":2793,"text":"and this little white dog called Maui"},{"time":5033,"text":"was staying with me."},{"time":6918,"text":"Half the city was dark because of a power cut,"},{"time":9390,"text":"and I was living on the dark side."},{"time":11614,"text":"Now, Maui was terrified of the dark,"},{"time":13723,"text":"so I had to carry him up the stairs,"},{"time":15827,"text":"actually down the stairs first, for his walk,"},{"time":18915,"text":"and then bring him back up."},{"time":20803,"text":"I was also hauling gallons of bottles of water"},{"time":23784,"text":"up to the seventh floor every day."},{"time":25883,"text":"And through all of this,"},{"time":27456,"text":"I had to hold a torch between my teeth."},{"time":29760,"text":"The stores nearby were out of flashlights"},{"time":32404,"text":"and batteries and bread."},{"time":35341,"text":"For a shower, I walked 40 blocks"},{"time":38004,"text":"to a branch of my gym."}]},{"cues":[{"time":39978,"text":"But these were not the major preoccupations of my day."},{"time":43057,"text":"It was just as critical for me to be the first person in"},{"time":46358,"text":"at a cafe nearby with extension cords and chargers"},{"time":49650,"text":"to juice my multiple devices."},{"time":51499,"text":"I started to prospect under the benches of bakeries"},{"time":54224,"text":"and the entrances of pastry shops for plug points."},{"time":57849,"text":"I wasn't the only one."},{"time":59418,"text":"Even in the rain, people stood between Madison and 5th Avenue"},{"time":63182,"text":"under their umbrellas charging their cell phones"},{"time":65646,"text":"from outlets on the street."},{"time":67683,"text":"Nature had just reminded us"},{"time":69940,"text":"that it was stronger than all our technology,"},{"time":72256,"text":"and yet here we were, obsessed about being wired."}]},{"cues":[{"time":75525,"text":"I think there's nothing like a crisis"},{"time":77401,"text":"to tell you what's really important and what's not,"},{"time":80590,"text":"and Sandy made me realize that our devices"},{"time":84152,"text":"and their connectivity matter to us"},{"time":86418,"text":"right up there with food and shelter."},{"time":90936,"text":"The self as we once knew it no longer exists,"},{"time":94253,"text":"and I think that an abstract, digital universe"},{"time":96745,"text":"has become a part of our identity,"},{"time":99270,"text":"and I want to talk to you about what I think that means."}]},{"cues":[{"time":103522,"text":"I'm a novelist, and I'm interested in the self"},{"time":106365,"text":"because the self and fiction have a lot in common."},{"time":108834,"text":"They're both stories, interpretations."},{"time":112151,"text":"You and I can experience things without a story."},{"time":114604,"text":"We might run up the stairs too quickly"},{"time":116686,"text":"and we might get breathless."},{"time":118373,"text":"But the larger sense that we have of our lives,"},{"time":120903,"text":"the slightly more abstract one, is indirect."},{"time":124263,"text":"Our story of our life is based on direct experience,"},{"time":127383,"text":"but it's embellished."},{"time":129277,"text":"A novel needs scene after scene to build,"},{"time":132125,"text":"and the story of our life needs an arc as well."},{"time":135273,"text":"It needs months and years."},{"time":137964,"text":"Discrete moments from our lives are its chapters."},{"time":140982,"text":"But the story is not about these chapters."},{"time":143572,"text":"It's the whole book."},{"time":145517,"text":"It's not only about the heartbreak and the happiness,"},{"time":148860,"text":"the victories and the disappointments,"},{"time":151039,"text":"but it's because how because of these,"},{"time":153244,"text":"and sometimes, more importantly, in spite of these,"},{"time":156397,"text":"we find our place in the world"},{"time":158492,"text":"and we change it and we change ourselves."},{"time":161572,"text":"Our story, therefore, needs two dimensions of time:"},{"time":164965,"text":"a long arc of time that is our lifespan,"},{"time":167980,"text":"and the timeframe of direct experience"},{"time":170483,"text":"that is the moment."},{"time":171936,"text":"Now the self that experiences directly"},{"time":174066,"text":"can only exist in the moment,"},{"time":175967,"text":"but the one that narrates needs several moments,"},{"time":178729,"text":"a whole sequence of them,"},{"time":180843,"text":"and that's why our full sense of self"},{"time":183088,"text":"needs both immersive experience"},{"time":186020,"text":"and the flow of time."},{"time":188465,"text":"Now, the flow of time is embedded in everything,"},{"time":191614,"text":"in the erosion of a grain of sand,"},{"time":194182,"text":"in the budding of a little bud into a rose."},{"time":197974,"text":"Without it, we would have no music."},{"time":200509,"text":"Our own emotions and state of mind"},{"time":202547,"text":"often encode time,"},{"time":204660,"text":"regret or nostalgia about the past,"},{"time":207218,"text":"hope or dread about the future."}]},{"cues":[{"time":210718,"text":"I think that technology has altered that flow of time."},{"time":214663,"text":"The overall time that we have for our narrative,"},{"time":217186,"text":"our lifespan, has been increasing,"},{"time":219360,"text":"but the smallest measure, the moment, has shrunk."},{"time":222477,"text":"It has shrunk because our instruments enable us"},{"time":224813,"text":"in part to measure smaller and smaller units of time,"},{"time":228073,"text":"and this in turn has given us a more granular understanding"},{"time":231343,"text":"of the material world,"},{"time":233216,"text":"and this granular understanding"},{"time":234652,"text":"has generated reams of data"},{"time":236955,"text":"that our brains can no longer comprehend"},{"time":239316,"text":"and for which we need more and more complicated computers."},{"time":242751,"text":"All of this to say that the gap"},{"time":245025,"text":"between what we can perceive and what we can measure"},{"time":247606,"text":"is only going to widen."},{"time":249528,"text":"Science can do things with and in a picosecond,"},{"time":252564,"text":"but you and I are never going to have the inner experience"},{"time":255267,"text":"of a millionth of a millionth of a second."},{"time":258453,"text":"You and I answer only to nature's rhythm and flow,"},{"time":262495,"text":"to the sun, the moon and the seasons,"},{"time":265434,"text":"and this is why we need that long arc of time"},{"time":268174,"text":"with the past, the present and the future"},{"time":270403,"text":"to see things for what they are,"},{"time":272167,"text":"to separate signal from noise"},{"time":274010,"text":"and the self from sensations."},{"time":276566,"text":"We need time's arrow to understand cause and effect,"},{"time":280175,"text":"not just in the material world,"},{"time":281930,"text":"but in our own intentions and our motivations."},{"time":285220,"text":"What happens when that arrow goes awry?"},{"time":289210,"text":"What happens when time warps?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":292694,"text":"So many of us today have the sensation"},{"time":294643,"text":"that time's arrow is pointing everywhere"},{"time":296887,"text":"and nowhere at once."},{"time":299152,"text":"This is because time doesn't flow in the digital world"},{"time":301839,"text":"in the same way that it does in the natural one."},{"time":305828,"text":"We all know that the Internet has shrunk space"},{"time":308528,"text":"as well as time."},{"time":309758,"text":"Far away over there is now here."},{"time":312071,"text":"News from India is a stream on my smartphone app"},{"time":314800,"text":"whether I'm in New York or New Delhi."},{"time":317679,"text":"And that's not all."},{"time":319114,"text":"Your last job, your dinner reservations from last year,"},{"time":321583,"text":"your former friends, lie on a flat plain with today's friends,"},{"time":324859,"text":"because the Internet also archives,"},{"time":326994,"text":"and it warps the past."},{"time":328788,"text":"With no distinction left between the past,"},{"time":330938,"text":"the present and the future, and the here or there,"},{"time":334210,"text":"we are left with this moment everywhere,"},{"time":338026,"text":"this moment that I'll call the digital now."}]},{"cues":[{"time":340450,"text":"Just how can we prioritize"},{"time":342618,"text":"in the landscape of the digital now?"},{"time":344977,"text":"This digital now is not the present,"},{"time":346882,"text":"because it's always a few seconds ahead,"},{"time":348935,"text":"with Twitter streams that are already trending"},{"time":350768,"text":"and news from other time zones."},{"time":352745,"text":"This isn't the now of a shooting pain in your foot"},{"time":355455,"text":"or the second that you bite into a pastry"},{"time":357943,"text":"or the three hours that you lose yourself in a great book."},{"time":361280,"text":"This now bears very little physical"},{"time":363132,"text":"or psychological reference to our own state."},{"time":366073,"text":"Its focus, instead, is to distract us"},{"time":368333,"text":"at every turn on the road."},{"time":370283,"text":"Every digital landmark is an invitation"},{"time":372454,"text":"to leave what you are doing now to go somewhere else"},{"time":374869,"text":"and do something else."},{"time":376488,"text":"Are you reading an interview by an author?"},{"time":378481,"text":"Why not buy his book? Tweet it. Share it."},{"time":381121,"text":"Like it. Find other books exactly like his."},{"time":383850,"text":"Find other people reading those books."},{"time":386718,"text":"Travel can be liberating,"},{"time":388762,"text":"but when it is incessant, we become"},{"time":390523,"text":"permanent exiles without repose."},{"time":392750,"text":"Choice is freedom, but not when it's constantly"},{"time":395494,"text":"for its own sake."}]},{"cues":[{"time":397541,"text":"Not just is the digital now far from the present,"},{"time":400129,"text":"but it's in direct competition with it,"},{"time":402791,"text":"and this is because not just am I absent from it,"},{"time":405173,"text":"but so are you."},{"time":406266,"text":"Not just are we absent from it, but so is everyone else."},{"time":409057,"text":"And therein lies its greatest convenience and horror."},{"time":412747,"text":"I can order foreign language books in the middle of the night,"},{"time":415575,"text":"shop for Parisian macarons,"},{"time":417374,"text":"and leave video messages that get picked up later."},{"time":419831,"text":"At all times, I can operate"},{"time":421806,"text":"at a different rhythm and pace from you,"},{"time":424042,"text":"while I sustain the illusion"},{"time":425959,"text":"that I'm tapped into you in real time."}]},{"cues":[{"time":429487,"text":"Sandy was a reminder"},{"time":431096,"text":"of how such an illusion can shatter."},{"time":433201,"text":"There were those with power and water,"},{"time":435065,"text":"and those without."},{"time":436561,"text":"There are those who went back to their lives,"},{"time":438894,"text":"and those who are still displaced"},{"time":440931,"text":"after so many months."},{"time":443286,"text":"For some reason, technology seems to perpetuate"},{"time":445988,"text":"the illusion for those who have it that everyone does,"},{"time":449434,"text":"and then, like an ironic slap in the face,"},{"time":452062,"text":"it makes it true."},{"time":454180,"text":"For example, it's said that there are more people"},{"time":455857,"text":"in India with access to cell phones than toilets."},{"time":458991,"text":"Now if this rift, which is already so great"},{"time":461413,"text":"in many parts of the world,"},{"time":462875,"text":"between the lack of infrastructure and the spread of technology,"},{"time":466230,"text":"isn't somehow bridged,"},{"time":467812,"text":"there will be ruptures between the digital"},{"time":469863,"text":"and the real."},{"time":472038,"text":"For us as individuals who live in the digital now"},{"time":475676,"text":"and spend most of our waking moments in it,"},{"time":478155,"text":"the challenge is to live in two streams of time"},{"time":480332,"text":"that are parallel and almost simultaneous."},{"time":483276,"text":"How does one live inside distraction?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":487376,"text":"We might think that those younger than us,"},{"time":489326,"text":"those who are born into this, will adapt more naturally."},{"time":492940,"text":"Possibly, but I remember my childhood."},{"time":496078,"text":"I remember my grandfather revising"},{"time":497782,"text":"the capitals of the world with me."},{"time":500044,"text":"Buda and Pest were separated by the Danube,"},{"time":502794,"text":"and Vienna had a Spanish riding school."},{"time":505569,"text":"If I were a child today, I could easily learn this information"},{"time":508468,"text":"with apps and hyperlinks,"},{"time":510633,"text":"but it really wouldn't be the same,"},{"time":512544,"text":"because much later, I went to Vienna,"},{"time":514824,"text":"and I went to the Spanish riding school,"},{"time":516792,"text":"and I could feel my grandfather right beside me."},{"time":520157,"text":"Night after night, he took me up on the terrace,"},{"time":522727,"text":"on his shoulders, and pointed out Jupiter"},{"time":525505,"text":"and Saturn and the Great Bear to me."},{"time":528733,"text":"And even here, when I look at the Great Bear,"},{"time":531428,"text":"I get back that feeling of being a child,"},{"time":534184,"text":"hanging onto his head and trying to balance myself"},{"time":536562,"text":"on his shoulder,"},{"time":538782,"text":"and I can get back that feeling of being a child again."},{"time":541982,"text":"What I had with my grandfather was wrapped"},{"time":544449,"text":"so often in information and knowledge and fact,"},{"time":547691,"text":"but it was about so much more"},{"time":549715,"text":"than information or knowledge or fact."},{"time":553505,"text":"Time-warping technology challenges"},{"time":555629,"text":"our deepest core,"},{"time":557581,"text":"because we are able to archive the past"},{"time":561348,"text":"and some of it becomes hard to forget,"},{"time":564589,"text":"even as the current moment"},{"time":567193,"text":"is increasingly unmemorable."},{"time":569812,"text":"We want to clutch, and we are left instead"},{"time":572552,"text":"clutching at a series of static moments."},{"time":575015,"text":"They're like soap bubbles that disappear when we touch them."}]},{"cues":[{"time":577721,"text":"By archiving everything, we think that we can store it,"},{"time":580514,"text":"but time is not data."},{"time":582479,"text":"It cannot be stored."},{"time":584612,"text":"You and I know exactly what it means like"},{"time":586628,"text":"to be truly present in a moment."},{"time":588532,"text":"It might have happened while we were"},{"time":589749,"text":"playing an instrument,"},{"time":591508,"text":"or looking into the eyes of someone we've known"},{"time":593356,"text":"for a very long time."},{"time":595540,"text":"At such moments, our selves are complete."},{"time":598571,"text":"The self that lives in the long narrative arc"},{"time":600639,"text":"and the self that experiences the moment"},{"time":602722,"text":"become one."},{"time":604114,"text":"The present encapsulates the past"},{"time":606056,"text":"and a promise for the future."},{"time":608487,"text":"The present joins a flow of time"},{"time":610455,"text":"from before and after."}]},{"cues":[{"time":612698,"text":"I first experienced these feelings with my grandmother."},{"time":616255,"text":"I wanted to learn to skip, and she found an old rope"},{"time":618594,"text":"and she tucked up her sari"},{"time":619946,"text":"and she jumped over it."},{"time":621674,"text":"I wanted to learn to cook, and she kept me in the kitchen,"},{"time":624328,"text":"cutting, cubing and chopping for a whole month."},{"time":628436,"text":"My grandmother taught me that things happen"},{"time":630843,"text":"in the time they take, that time can't be fought,"},{"time":634564,"text":"and because it will pass and it will move,"},{"time":636397,"text":"we owe the present moment our full attention."},{"time":639511,"text":"Attention is time."},{"time":642155,"text":"One of my yoga instructors once said"},{"time":644338,"text":"that love is attention,"},{"time":646581,"text":"and definitely from my grandmother,"},{"time":648415,"text":"love and attention were one and the same thing."},{"time":652741,"text":"The digital world cannibalizes time,"},{"time":655324,"text":"and in doing so, I want to suggest"},{"time":658704,"text":"that what it threatens"},{"time":660378,"text":"is the completeness of ourselves."},{"time":662808,"text":"It threatens the flow of love."},{"time":665166,"text":"But we don't need to let it."},{"time":667187,"text":"We can choose otherwise."},{"time":668655,"text":"We've seen again and again"},{"time":670732,"text":"just how creative technology can be,"},{"time":672962,"text":"and in our lives and in our actions,"},{"time":675202,"text":"we can choose those solutions and those innovations"},{"time":679191,"text":"and those moments that restore the flow of time"},{"time":682299,"text":"instead of fragmenting it."},{"time":685920,"text":"We can slow down and we can tune in"},{"time":688500,"text":"to the ebb and flow of time."},{"time":691172,"text":"We can choose to take time back."}]},{"cues":[{"time":695120,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":697320,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}